---
title: Spiced Beef Strips & Creamy Leek Sauce with Potato Mash & Garlic Veggies
description: There’s only one soulmate sauce for tender beef strips and that’s a creamy sauce. Add some leek to this creamy .dream and drizzle it over to serve beside a cheerful mash for a night of comfort in a bowl.
